  "translations": {
    "en": "When the Prophet was informed of this, he said to his companions: Charity increases a person's wealth, so give charity and Allah will have mercy on you. And humility elevates a person's rank, so be humble and Allah will elevate you. And forgiveness increases a person's honor, so forgive and Allah will honor you.",
    "ur": "جب نبی کو یہ بات پہنچی تو آپ نے فرمایا:",
    "tr": "Bu haber Peygamber'e ulaşınca dedi:",
    "fa": "وقتی این خبر به پیامبر رسید، فرمود:",
    "id": "Ketika berita ini sampai kepada Nabi, beliau bersabda:",
    "bn": "নবী এই খবর শুনে বললেন:",
    "es": "Cuando el Profeta fue informado, dijo:",
    "fr": "Quand le Prophète en fut informé, il dit :",
